  "title": "詠唱しやすい",
  "created": 1778900233,
  "updated": 1778901746,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a07dd06751c34eae35149c8",
      "text": "詠唱しやすい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778900233,
      "updated": 1778900233
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07dd08000000000099edf6",
      "text": " 魔術を行使するために呪文を詠唱するとき、文言は短いほど口にしやすい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778900233,
      "updated": 1778900546
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07ddda000000000099edfb",
      "text": "  上級者は短縮した呪文を使う",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778900442,
      "updated": 1778901746
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07de0a000000000099edfd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778900490,
      "updated": 1778900490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07de0a000000000099edfe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778900490,
      "updated": 1778900490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07de13000000000099ee00",
      "text": "敵に放つ技の技名を口上で言い放つときも技名が短いほど早い",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778900499,
      "updated": 1778900509
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07de1c000000000099ee01",
      "text": " 長いと攻撃を始めるまでに時間がかかる ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778900509,
      "updated": 1778900530
    },
